OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start in places but
OL,6,Fsunny spells quickly developing
OL,7,Fleading to a largely dry and bright
OL,8,Fmorning. Throughout the afternoon
OL,9,Fcloud will build with some showers
OL,10,Fdeveloping later, possibly turning
OL,11,Fheavy in places. Warm in any sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny lingering showers fading
OL,14,Faway, with the best of any clearer
OL,15,Fskies towards the west. A few spot of
OL,16,Fdrizzle possible in the east overnight
OL,17,Fbut western areas remaining dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
