OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FRather grey with perhaps the
OL,6,Fodd spot of light rain in places,
OL,7,Fespecially over the hills. Some
OL,8,Fbrighter spells developing later in
OL,9,Fthe day, but feeling cooler than of
OL,10,Flate.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FEarly
OL,13,Fmorning cloud on Wednesday and
OL,14,FThursday quickly lifting to leave
OL,15,Fplenty of sunshine both days. Risk of
OL,16,Fshowers come Friday but feeling
OL,17,Fincreasingly warmer and more humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
